### Health check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@lexoria.com",
  "username": "LexoriaHero",
  "password": "password123",
  "age": 17
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@lexoria.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get my profile (paste your accessToken from login response)
GET http://localhost:3001/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJjbW4xdHpmazMwMDAweDRjaTQyc3JxOTJ3IiwiZW1haWwiOiJ0ZXN0QGxleG9yaWEuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc0MTg4NzA0LCJleHAiOjE3NzQxODk2MDR9.qvfFRSEjIL1ycacu341KaGjJJxC6kfl7oqWoDxJvX54

